Description:
Telit Wireless Solutions is an enabler of the global machine-to-machine (m2m) movement. The company views m2m as the space intersected by the following three technology pillars
Long-range cellular connection of devices to each-other and the Internet of Things (IoT);
Short-range license free wireless connection of devices to their peripherals, to each other, and to long-range gateways;
Position awareness for all connected devices.
